---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import contact from "../data/contact.json";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Imprint"
  description="Imprint and privacy note for michael-giang portfolio — responsible person, contact and how this static site handles data."
>
  <h1>Imprint</h1>

  <div class="prose imprint">
    <h2>Responsible for this website</h2>
    <p>
      Michael Giang<br />
      Zurich, Switzerland<br />
      <a href={`mailto:${contact.email}`}>{contact.email}</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      This is a personal, non-commercial portfolio. Source code:
      <a href="https://github.com/mgiang95/mgiang95.github.io"
        >github.com/mgiang95</a
      >
    </p>

    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      This site is intentionally boring about data: it is a static website
      with <strong>no cookies, no analytics and no tracking</strong> of any
      kind.
    </p>
    <p>
      Your theme preferences (hue, color scheme, density) are stored in your
      browser's <code>localStorage</code> — they never leave your device and
      you can remove them at any time by clearing site data.
    </p>
    <p>
      The site is hosted on GitHub Pages. GitHub may process technical
      server logs (such as IP addresses) to operate the service; see the
      <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement"
        >GitHub Privacy Statement</a
      >. No log data is available to or used by me.
    </p>
    <p>
      External links (GitHub, LinkedIn, linked articles) lead to services
      with their own privacy policies.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .imprint {
    margin-block-start: var(--space-stack-lg);
    max-width: 65ch;
  }
</style>
